successes.title: THAMES BATHS LIDO - for swimming, for relaxing, for everyone
successes.description: THAMES BATHS LIDO is a new swimming and cultural destination for London on the River Thames using clean, filtered & heated Thames water

Pledges.description: A big virtual thank you from us and the knowledge that you have been a big part of turning this idea from architectural vision into urban reality.
A token for one swim at any time in the first year at Thames Baths lido.
Two tokens for a swim, perhaps two for you or one for you and your favourite swimming partner, at any time in the first year at Thames Baths lido.
We've listened to your requests for prints...
At £30 you can get a beautiful A4 photographic print of the Thames Baths at Temple Stairs, Victoria Embankment. It will be a great talking point whether it's at home or at work.
Each print will be individually numbered and these are limited to 100 prints, so you'll know everytime you see it that you've made a great and unique contribution to the project.
By pledging £45 you'll become a Red founding member. Limited to 500 members. You'll also get:
+ Red Membership Card, designed by graphic designers Build

+ A4 photographic print of selected image from Thames Baths 
+ A soon to be famous Red Thames Baths swimming cap
Give a gift of RED Membership to a friend
By pledging £50 you'll be able to gift a RED membership to a friend, whilst also receiving a swimming token for you (so you can swim together at least once).
Limited to 50 gifts. You friend will get:
+ Red Membership Card, designed by graphic designers Build
